OL,6,GIf you were watching ITV 1's quiz show
OL,7,GThe 1% Club last night, you may have
OL,8,Gfaced a little puzzle of another sort.
OL,10,FThe show's "commercial" breaks were
OL,11,Fall packed with trailers.
OL,13,FOf course, most Pres enthusiasts and
OL,14,Fregular readers of this website know
OL,15,Fexactly why this was.
