OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FITV 1, Channel 4 and Channel 5 can
OL,7,Fonly run 40 minutes of ads between 6pm
OL,8,Fand 11pm but can run up to 12 minutes
OL,9,Fin any one hour. This mean leaving
OL,10,Fsome hours light or empty so more ads
OL,11,Fcan be packed around the most popular
OL,12,For lucrative shows.
OL,14,FDuring the week it can at least be
OL,15,Fargued that there is a benefit to
OL,16,Fviewers ` it means fewer ads during
OL,17,Fthe news. This is one reason why Ofcom
OL,18,Frecently surprised many when it kicked
OL,19,Fplans to allow the PSBs to run as many
OL,20,Fads as the other commercial channels
OL,21,Finto the long grass.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
