OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FBut at the weekend there is nothing
OL,7,Fwhich can conceivably be described as
OL,8,Fa benefit to the public.
OL,10,FITV, STV and Channel 4 wanted the
OL,11,Frules to change ` Channel 5's parent
OL,12,Fcompany was opposed.
OL,14,FTrailer breaks are simply irritating
OL,15,Fand repetitive. The vast majority of
OL,16,Fviewers probably imagine that the
OL,17,Fadvertising time has gone unsold `
OL,18,Fhardly a positive reflection on the
OL,19,Fprogramme.
