OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FOfcom now intends to look at the issue
OL,7,Fholistically ` also taking into
OL,8,Faccount issues such as the renewal of
OL,9,Fthe licences for ITV and Channel 5 and
OL,10,Fthe Media Bill which is set to become
OL,11,Flaw before the General Election.
OL,13,FThere has been no public discussion as
OL,14,Ffar as I am aware over whether there
OL,15,Fshould be changes to ITV 1's specific
OL,16,Fpublic service obligations in the new
OL,17,Flicence period which starts in January
OL,18,F2025.
