OL,3,COfcom ad rules and ITV regional/
OL,4,Cnational news requirements
OL,6,FBut even so, this is a hypothetical at
OL,7,Fpresent ` ITV 1 overdelivers on its
OL,8,Fnational news commitments by a country
OL,9,Fmile with the hour long 6.30pm
OL,10,Fprogramme plus News at Ten.
OL,12,FRecent trading updates from both ITV
OL,13,Fplc and STV highlighted the tough
OL,14,Fenvironment for advertising sales.
OL,16,FThe economic situation together with
OL,17,Fthe shift online by some advertisers
OL,18,Fis something of a perfect storm.
OL,20,FOfcom needs to hurry up and look again
OL,21,Fat the current restrictions.
